Achievements.Name: No Way Back
Achievements.Description: Complete the mission Shattered Hopes in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Coffee Break
Achievements.Description: Complete the mission Morning Coffee in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Prison Break
Achievements.Description: Complete the mission Alliances in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Clay Jungle
Achievements.Description: Complete the mission Urban Nightmare in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Urban Liberty
Achievements.Description: Complete the mission Ferry of Styx in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Trapped
Achievements.Description: Complete the mission Wet Dusk in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Joint Venture
Achievements.Description: Complete the mission Revenge in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Trojan Horse
Achievements.Description: Complete the mission Ruins of Amazonia in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: We're Outta Here!
Achievements.Description: Complete the single player campaign on any difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Faithful Companion
Achievements.Description: Successfully complete all missions in the cooperative multi-player campaign on any difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Buddy Tag
Achievements.Description: Successfully complete a mission in cooperative mode.

Achievements.Name: Exotic Parts
Achievements.Description: Kill 20 enemy soldiers by explosions.

Achievements.Name: Living Thunderbolt
Achievements.Description: Successfully use the Flash grenade skill 10 times.

Achievements.Name: Clean Sweep
Achievements.Description: Complete any of the missions without using any skill ammo.

Achievements.Name: Bullet Magnet
Achievements.Description: One of your squad members has been incapacitated more than 11 times.

Achievements.Name: Superior Marksman
Achievements.Description: Deliver a headshot in FPS mode from over 75 meters.

Achievements.Name: Bounty Hunter
Achievements.Description: Deliver 50 lethal headshots.

Achievements.Name: Experienced Commander
Achievements.Description: Complete 5 missions in veteran difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Protector
Achievements.Description: No one got incapacitated at the clearing defense in Village Attack. Veteran difficulty required.

Achievements.Name: Skilled Tactician
Achievements.Description: Acquire the machinegun nest in mission Shattered Hopes and kill 5 enemy soldiers with it.

Achievements.Name: King of the Labyrinth
Achievements.Description: Kill Rodriguez in mission Morning Coffee.

Achievements.Name: Cannon Fodder
Achievements.Description: No one got incapacitated at the grenade trap in Morning Coffee. Regular difficulty required.

Achievements.Name: Stealth Approach
Achievements.Description: Get to the gates without being detected in mission Alliances.

Achievements.Name: Anti-sniper
Achievements.Description: Kill the sniper in mission Urban Nightmare before he notices you. Veteran difficulty required.

Achievements.Name: Alliance
Achievements.Description: None of the escorting Brazilian soldiers die in mission Urban Nightmare.

Achievements.Name: Kill the Source
Achievements.Description: Destroy all 3 enemy troop carriers in mission Ferry of Styx.

Achievements.Name: Tank Top
Achievements.Description: You used the tanker truck to eliminate the defenders at the square in mission Ferry of Styx.

Achievements.Name: Elite Hunter
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 of the bases elite defender soldiers in mission Revenge.

Achievements.Name: Survivor
Achievements.Description: Complete mission Revenge without letting any of your squad members become incapacitated.

Achievements.Name: Amateur Archeologist
Achievements.Description: Complete mission Ruins of Amazonia without damaging the dig site.

Achievements.Name: Bombastic
Achievements.Description: Blow up at least 5 vehicles in mission Wet Dusk.

Achievements.Name: Supervisor
Achievements.Description: No enemy soldiers get to the workers in mission Ruins of Amazonia. Veteran difficulty required.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Soldier
Achievements.Description: The elite guards of Juarez cant incapacitate any of your squad members in mission Boys Meet Girl.

Achievements.Name: Reunion
Achievements.Description: Reunite the squads in mission Touchdown.

Achievements.Name: Merciless
Achievements.Description: Kill all fleeing enemies after you defended the village in the Prologue.

Achievements.Name: Cleaner
Achievements.Description: Kill all enemies at the plantation in mission Morning Coffee.

Achievements.Name: Expert Charger
Achievements.Description: Get through the ruins in Shattered Hopes before the militia catches up. Veteran difficulty required.

Achievements.Name: Jeep Killer
Achievements.Description: Use your first rocket to kill the jeep in mission Touchdown. Regular difficulty required.

Achievements.Name: Safe SAM Stroll
Achievements.Description: Get to the SAM site without getting incapacitated after Point Alpha in mission Touchdown.

Achievements.Name: Tough Kid
Achievements.Description: No Infiltrator member went down while at the camp in Village Attack. Regular difficulty required.

Achievements.Name: King of the Hill
Achievements.Description: Complete the village defense objective without leaving the village square in the Prologue.

Achievements.Name: Rock Solid
Achievements.Description: Keep the enemy away from the civilians in mission Alliances. Veteran difficulty required.

Achievements.Name: Woodsman
Achievements.Description: Complete Wet Dusk without any of your squads becoming incapacitated. Regular difficulty required.
